          <title>Partial view of .regsp text file data. Details of <italic toggle="yes">Heterosigma akashiwo</italic> gene alignment against the first two references are highlighted: <bold>a</bold>, query sequence; <bold>b</bold>, total count of contig genes against a reference; <bold>c</bold>, gene information; <bold>d</bold>, nucleotide sequence of the query matching the gene; <bold>e</bold>, detailed BLASTX information, such as sequence position in the query, alignment length, bit score, and translation frame; and <bold>f</bold>, alignment of each gene with translated query.</title>
        </caption>
